o the Einstein-Laub force\ndensity [Phys. Rev. Lett 111, 043602 (2013)], our rebuttal may also shed light\non the controversy over the momentum of light.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Dec 2013 22:18:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 May 2014 20:57:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-15"}
