ar dichroism (RIXS-MCD) extends the possibilities of standard\nmagnetic characterization tools.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Dec 2013 10:25:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Jan 2014 12:05:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-01-20"}
